   "source": [
    "2. What happens when a class statement's top level contains a basic assignment statement?\n",
    "answer-When class statement's top level contains a basic assignment statement, it is considered as class attribute. \n",
    "    Change in the value of class attribute will affect all the instances of the class."
   ]
